#
# entry 7_39 of theta-curves table of Moriuchi
# equivalent to either HK5_2 or HK6_13 as a handlebody
# after an IH followed by Reidemeister V we obtain
# embedding 6+150_23 in the bigtree. This in turn
# is nonminimal after an IH followed by moving a strand
# from a triple node and finally a fork move.
# Hence it is equivalent to HK5_2
#
knot {
 ^ ^ ^ ;
| X X |;
|| |h||;
 x x|x ;
||| y||;
| X X |;
 U U U ;
}
